data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Cape Coral! This stunning 1-year-old home is situated on a spacious corner lot, offering the perfect blend of Smart Home-Ready Technology and ultimate comfort and convenience.  Imagine enjoying the benefits of last year's interest rate on the Assumable Mortgage - an incredible opportunity for qualified buyers! Constructed by DR Horton, this home boasts $50K worth of upgrades, ensuring top-notch quality and style.  The meticulous attention to detail is evident throughout, from the top-of-the-line insulation to the pet amenities. The spacious floor plan features gigantic walk-in closets and dual linen closets.  The extra energy-efficient insulation in all inside walls, soffits, and foam insulation around all electrical outlet boxes ensures that your monthly electrical bill will be around only $200!  The 3-car garage includes an energy-efficient AC/heating unit, perfect for keeping your vehicles comfortable year-round. Located near excellent schools, this home is ideal for families. Seller is relocating out of state and is motivated, presenting a great opportunity for investors.
